{"tid":1052056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國婦住院逾3年未付分毫     醫管局入稟追討逾600萬","createTime":"2019-03-08T04:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T11:56:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b71424612e54acf6e7c6c5b69af8a60cb39c3f73","tid":1052056,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"本港公立醫院資源緊絀，病床使用率超過100%，病人逼爆病房。有內地婦於2015年發生交通意外後被送往伊利沙伯醫院治療，及後轉往九龍醫院，至今一直以醫院為家，但未付分毫，拖欠醫管局逾600萬醫療費。醫管局昨入稟高院，向該病人索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告是醫院管理局，被告胡怀娇，屬精神沒行為能力人士，聯絡地址包括九龍秀茂坪邨、以及大埔一私人單位。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀透露，被告的女兒兼監護人Hu Errong曾就被告的交通意外取得法援，並於2017年入稟向肇事司機索償，案件已排期2020年開審。<br />\n<br />\n至於本案，被告於2015年11月11日因交通意外被送往伊利沙伯醫院治療，及後於2017年8月9日被轉往九龍醫院，她住院至今。直至今年2月28日，被告已拖欠617萬元醫療費用，以及自今年3月1日起，每天拖欠醫療費5,100元。<br />\n<br />\n院方多次向被告追討欠款不果，而自3月1日起，九龍醫院更每隔3至4天便向被告發出賬單，但對方拒絕支付或無能力支付，醫管局遂入稟循法律途徑追討。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA377/19】<br />\n<br />\n記者楊思雅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59344284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59344284&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMsQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=95483947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59344284&h=4b6e78a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59344284</a>"},{"pid":"38d805ac173f13b722f5adc4f515943969a63da2","tid":1052056,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"大埔一私人單位<br />\n夠鐘賣樓了"},{"pid":"00f9ee771534ae78a59ffd6badfcecea0d2e0128","tid":1052056,"uid":198216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"告到佢破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0281f6ba159b5bd5a07e6ce0acfa2e22b6ee322e","tid":1052056,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:48:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eb3eedfbd61895c378055ec4c016d03de122868","tid":1052056,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"有冇機會強制沒收樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4439d31600e9903b54ed27e57b46f2fe1a9e2552","tid":1052056,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"支那婆9成9會放生"}]}